reviewText: What a feast for the eyes!  The color was first rate, the music evocative of the scenery, and I have watched it at least half a dozen times since I got it.  Now if I can just find a way to get there!  My only complaint is that 10 minutes is way too short!
Beautiful video of a fantastic place, but again much much too short.  I fell in love with Peterhof and now I can revisit whenever----
